{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"The global challenge that I want to talk to you about today"},{"time":4000,"text":"rarely makes the front pages."},{"time":6000,"text":"It, however, is enormous"},{"time":9000,"text":"in both scale and importance."},{"time":12000,"text":"Look, you all are very well traveled;"},{"time":15000,"text":"this is TEDGlobal after all."},{"time":17000,"text":"But I do hope to take you to some places"},{"time":19000,"text":"you've never been to before."}]},{"cues":[{"time":21000,"text":"So, let's start off in China."},{"time":23000,"text":"This photo was taken two weeks ago."},{"time":26000,"text":"Actually, one indication is that little boy on my husband's shoulders"},{"time":29000,"text":"has just graduated from high school."},{"time":31000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":33000,"text":"But this is Tiananmen Square."},{"time":35000,"text":"Many of you have been there. It's not the real China."},{"time":38000,"text":"Let me take you to the real China."},{"time":40000,"text":"This is in the Dabian Mountains"},{"time":42000,"text":"in the remote part of Hubei province in central China."},{"time":46000,"text":"Dai Manju is 13 years old at the time the story starts."},{"time":49000,"text":"She lives with her parents,"},{"time":51000,"text":"her two brothers and her great-aunt."},{"time":54000,"text":"They have a hut that has no electricity,"},{"time":56000,"text":"no running water,"},{"time":58000,"text":"no wristwatch, no bicycle."},{"time":60000,"text":"And they share this great splendor"},{"time":62000,"text":"with a very large pig."},{"time":65000,"text":"Dai Manju was in sixth grade when her parents said,"},{"time":68000,"text":"\"We're going to pull you out of school"},{"time":70000,"text":"because the 13-dollar school fees are too much for us."},{"time":73000,"text":"You're going to be spending the rest of your life in the rice paddies."},{"time":75000,"text":"Why would we waste this money on you?\""},{"time":77000,"text":"This is what happens to girls in remote areas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80000,"text":"Turns out that Dai Manju was"},{"time":82000,"text":"the best pupil in her grade."},{"time":84000,"text":"She still made the two-hour trek to the schoolhouse"},{"time":87000,"text":"and tried to catch every little bit of information"},{"time":90000,"text":"that seeped out of the doors."},{"time":92000,"text":"We wrote about her in The New York Times."},{"time":94000,"text":"We got a flood of donations --"},{"time":97000,"text":"mostly 13-dollar checks"},{"time":100000,"text":"because New York Times readers are very generous"},{"time":102000,"text":"in tiny amounts"},{"time":104000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":106000,"text":"but then, we got a money transfer"},{"time":109000,"text":"for $10,000 --"},{"time":111000,"text":"really nice guy."},{"time":113000,"text":"We turned the money over to that man there, the principal of the school."},{"time":116000,"text":"He was delighted."},{"time":118000,"text":"He thought, \"Oh, I can renovate the school."},{"time":120000,"text":"I can give scholarships to all the girls,"},{"time":122000,"text":"you know, if they work hard and stay in school."},{"time":124000,"text":"So Dai Manju basically"},{"time":126000,"text":"finished out middle school."},{"time":128000,"text":"She went to high school."},{"time":130000,"text":"She went to vocational school for accounting."},{"time":132000,"text":"She scouted for jobs down in Guangdong province in the south."},{"time":135000,"text":"She found a job, she scouted for jobs"},{"time":137000,"text":"for her classmates and her friends."},{"time":139000,"text":"She sent money back to her family."},{"time":142000,"text":"They built a new house,"},{"time":144000,"text":"this time with running water,"},{"time":146000,"text":"electricity, a bicycle,"},{"time":148000,"text":"no pig."}]},{"cues":[{"time":150000,"text":"What we saw was a natural experiment."},{"time":153000,"text":"It is rare to get an exogenous investment"},{"time":155000,"text":"in girls' education."},{"time":157000,"text":"And over the years, as we followed Dai Manju, we were able to see"},{"time":160000,"text":"that she was able to move out of a vicious cycle"},{"time":163000,"text":"and into a virtuous cycle."},{"time":165000,"text":"She not only changed her own dynamic,"},{"time":167000,"text":"she changed her household, she changed her family, her village."},{"time":170000,"text":"The village became a real standout."},{"time":173000,"text":"Of course, most of China was flourishing at the time,"},{"time":176000,"text":"but they were able to get a road built"},{"time":179000,"text":"to link them up to the rest of China."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181000,"text":"And that brings me to my first major"},{"time":184000,"text":"of two tenets of \"Half the Sky.\""},{"time":186000,"text":"And that is that"},{"time":188000,"text":"the central moral challenge"},{"time":190000,"text":"of this century"},{"time":192000,"text":"is gender inequity."},{"time":194000,"text":"In the 19th century, it was slavery."},{"time":196000,"text":"In the 20th century, it was totalitarianism."},{"time":199000,"text":"The cause of our time"},{"time":201000,"text":"is the brutality that so many people"},{"time":203000,"text":"face around the world because of their gender."},{"time":206000,"text":"So some of you may be thinking,"},{"time":208000,"text":"\"Gosh, that's hyperbole."},{"time":210000,"text":"She's exaggerating.\""},{"time":212000,"text":"Well, let me ask you this question."},{"time":214000,"text":"How many of you think there are more males or more females in the world?"},{"time":217000,"text":"Let me take a poll. How many of you think there are more males in the world?"},{"time":220000,"text":"Hands up, please."},{"time":222000,"text":"How many of you think -- a few -- how many of you there are more females in the world?"},{"time":225000,"text":"Okay, most of you."},{"time":227000,"text":"Well, you know this latter group, you're wrong."},{"time":229000,"text":"There are, true enough,"},{"time":231000,"text":"in Europe and the West,"},{"time":233000,"text":"when women and men"},{"time":235000,"text":"have equal access to food and health care,"},{"time":237000,"text":"there are more women, we live longer."},{"time":239000,"text":"But in most of the rest of the world, that's not the case."},{"time":242000,"text":"In fact, demographers have shown"},{"time":244000,"text":"that there are anywhere between 60 million"},{"time":246000,"text":"and 100 million"},{"time":248000,"text":"missing females in the current population."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251000,"text":"And, you know, it happens for several reasons."},{"time":254000,"text":"For instance, in the last half-century,"},{"time":256000,"text":"more girls were discriminated to death"},{"time":259000,"text":"than all the people killed on all the battlefields"},{"time":261000,"text":"in the 20th century."},{"time":264000,"text":"Sometimes it's also because of the sonogram."},{"time":266000,"text":"Girls get aborted before they're even born"},{"time":269000,"text":"when there are scarce resources."},{"time":271000,"text":"This girl here, for instance,"},{"time":273000,"text":"is in a feeding center in Ethiopia."},{"time":275000,"text":"The entire center was filled with girls like her."},{"time":278000,"text":"What's remarkable is that her brothers, in the same family,"},{"time":281000,"text":"were totally fine."},{"time":283000,"text":"In India, in the first year of life,"},{"time":285000,"text":"from zero to one,"},{"time":287000,"text":"boy and girl babies basically survive at the same rate"},{"time":290000,"text":"because they depend upon the breast,"},{"time":292000,"text":"and the breast shows no son preference."},{"time":294000,"text":"From one to five,"},{"time":297000,"text":"girls die at a 50 percent higher mortality rate"},{"time":300000,"text":"than boys, in all of India."}]},{"cues":[{"time":303000,"text":"The second tenet of \"Half the Sky\""},{"time":306000,"text":"is that, let's put aside the morality of all the right and wrong of it all,"},{"time":309000,"text":"and just on a purely practical level,"},{"time":312000,"text":"we think that"},{"time":314000,"text":"one of the best ways to fight poverty and to fight terrorism"},{"time":317000,"text":"is to educate girls"},{"time":319000,"text":"and to bring women into the formal labor force."},{"time":322000,"text":"Poverty, for instance."},{"time":324000,"text":"There are three reasons why this is the case."},{"time":326000,"text":"For one, overpopulation is one of"},{"time":328000,"text":"the persistent causes of poverty."},{"time":331000,"text":"And you know, when you educate a boy,"},{"time":333000,"text":"his family tends to have fewer kids,"},{"time":335000,"text":"but only slightly."},{"time":337000,"text":"When you educate a girl,"},{"time":339000,"text":"she tends to have significantly fewer kids."},{"time":342000,"text":"The second reason is"},{"time":345000,"text":"it has to do with spending."},{"time":347000,"text":"It's kind of like the dirty, little secret of poverty,"},{"time":349000,"text":"which is that,"},{"time":351000,"text":"not only do poor people"},{"time":353000,"text":"take in very little income,"},{"time":355000,"text":"but also, the income that they take in,"},{"time":357000,"text":"they don't spend it very wisely,"},{"time":360000,"text":"and unfortunately, most of that spending is done by men."},{"time":363000,"text":"So research has shown,"},{"time":365000,"text":"if you look at people who live under two dollars a day --"},{"time":368000,"text":"one metric of poverty --"},{"time":370000,"text":"two percent of that take-home pay"},{"time":372000,"text":"goes to this basket here, in education."},{"time":375000,"text":"20 percent goes to a basket that is a combination of"},{"time":378000,"text":"alcohol, tobacco, sugary drinks --"},{"time":380000,"text":"and prostitution and festivals."},{"time":383000,"text":"If you just take four percentage points"},{"time":385000,"text":"and put it into this basket,"},{"time":387000,"text":"you would have a transformative effect."}]},{"cues":[{"time":391000,"text":"The last reason has to do"},{"time":393000,"text":"with women being part of the solution, not the problem."},{"time":396000,"text":"You need to use scarce resources."},{"time":398000,"text":"It's a waste of resources if you don't use someone like Dai Manju."},{"time":401000,"text":"Bill Gates put it very well"},{"time":403000,"text":"when he was traveling through Saudi Arabia."},{"time":405000,"text":"He was speaking to an audience much like yourselves."},{"time":408000,"text":"However, two-thirds of the way there was a barrier."},{"time":411000,"text":"On this side was men,"},{"time":413000,"text":"and then the barrier, and this side was women."},{"time":415000,"text":"And someone from this side of the room got up and said,"},{"time":417000,"text":"\"Mr. Gates, we have here as our goal in Saudi Arabia"},{"time":420000,"text":"to be one of the top 10 countries"},{"time":422000,"text":"when it comes to technology."},{"time":424000,"text":"Do you think we'll make it?\""},{"time":426000,"text":"So Bill Gates, as he was staring out at the audience, he said,"},{"time":429000,"text":"\"If you're not fully utilizing half the resources in your country,"},{"time":432000,"text":"there is no way you will get anywhere near the top 10.\""},{"time":435000,"text":"So here is Bill of Arabia."}]},{"cues":[{"time":438000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":440000,"text":"So what would some of the specific challenges"},{"time":442000,"text":"look like?"},{"time":445000,"text":"I would say, on the top of the agenda"},{"time":448000,"text":"is sex trafficking."},{"time":450000,"text":"And I'll just say two things about this."},{"time":452000,"text":"The slavery at the peak of the slave trade"},{"time":455000,"text":"in the 1780s:"},{"time":458000,"text":"there were about 80,000 slaves"},{"time":460000,"text":"transported from Africa to the New World."},{"time":463000,"text":"Now, modern slavery:"},{"time":466000,"text":"according to State Department rough statistics,"},{"time":469000,"text":"there are about 800,000 -- 10 times the number --"},{"time":472000,"text":"that are trafficked across international borders."},{"time":475000,"text":"And that does not even include those"},{"time":477000,"text":"that are trafficked within country borders,"},{"time":479000,"text":"which is a substantial portion."},{"time":482000,"text":"And if you look at"},{"time":484000,"text":"another factor, another contrast,"},{"time":487000,"text":"a slave back then is worth"},{"time":489000,"text":"about $40,000"},{"time":491000,"text":"in today's money."},{"time":493000,"text":"Today, you can buy a girl trafficked"},{"time":496000,"text":"for a few hundred dollars,"},{"time":498000,"text":"which means she's actually more disposable."},{"time":501000,"text":"But you know, there is progress being made"},{"time":504000,"text":"in places like Cambodia and Thailand."},{"time":506000,"text":"We don't have to expect a world"},{"time":508000,"text":"where girls are bought and sold or killed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":511000,"text":"The second item on the agenda"},{"time":513000,"text":"is maternal mortality."},{"time":516000,"text":"You know, childbirth in this part of the world"},{"time":519000,"text":"is a wonderful event."},{"time":521000,"text":"In Niger, one in seven women"},{"time":524000,"text":"can expect to die during childbirth."},{"time":527000,"text":"Around the world,"},{"time":529000,"text":"one woman dies every minute and a half from childbirth."},{"time":533000,"text":"You know, it's not as though"},{"time":535000,"text":"we don't have the technological solution,"},{"time":538000,"text":"but these women have three strikes against them:"},{"time":541000,"text":"they are poor, they are rural"},{"time":543000,"text":"and they are female."},{"time":546000,"text":"You know, for every woman who does die,"},{"time":548000,"text":"there are 20 who survive"},{"time":550000,"text":"but end up with an injury."},{"time":552000,"text":"And the most devastating injury"},{"time":554000,"text":"is obstetric fistula."},{"time":556000,"text":"It's a tearing during obstructed labor"},{"time":558000,"text":"that leaves a woman incontinent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":561000,"text":"Let me tell you about Mahabuba."},{"time":563000,"text":"She lives in Ethiopia."},{"time":565000,"text":"She was married against her will at age 13."},{"time":568000,"text":"She got pregnant, ran to the bush to have the baby,"},{"time":571000,"text":"but you know, her body was very immature,"},{"time":574000,"text":"and she ended up having obstructed labor."},{"time":577000,"text":"The baby died, and she ended up with a fistula."},{"time":580000,"text":"So that meant she was incontinent;"},{"time":582000,"text":"she couldn't control her wastes."},{"time":585000,"text":"In a word, she stank."},{"time":587000,"text":"The villagers thought she was cursed; they didn't know what to do with her."},{"time":590000,"text":"So finally, they put her at the edge of the village in a hut."},{"time":593000,"text":"They ripped off the door"},{"time":595000,"text":"so that the hyenas would get her at night."},{"time":598000,"text":"That night, there was a stick in the hut."},{"time":601000,"text":"She fought off the hyenas with that stick."},{"time":604000,"text":"And the next morning,"},{"time":606000,"text":"she knew if she could get to a nearby village where there was a foreign missionary,"},{"time":609000,"text":"she would be saved."},{"time":611000,"text":"Because she had some damage to her nerves,"},{"time":613000,"text":"she crawled all the way -- 30 miles --"},{"time":616000,"text":"to that doorstep, half dead."},{"time":619000,"text":"The foreign missionary opened the door,"},{"time":621000,"text":"knew exactly what had happened,"},{"time":623000,"text":"took her to a nearby fistula hospital in Addis Ababa,"},{"time":626000,"text":"and she was repaired"},{"time":628000,"text":"with a 350-dollar operation."},{"time":631000,"text":"The doctors and nurses there noticed"},{"time":633000,"text":"that she was not only a survivor,"},{"time":635000,"text":"she was really clever, and they made her a nurse."},{"time":638000,"text":"So now, Mahabuba,"},{"time":640000,"text":"she is saving the lives"},{"time":642000,"text":"of hundreds, thousands, of women."},{"time":644000,"text":"She has become part of the solution, not the problem."},{"time":646000,"text":"She's moved out of a vicious cycle"},{"time":648000,"text":"and into a virtuous cycle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":650000,"text":"I've talked about some of the challenges,"},{"time":653000,"text":"let me talk about some of the solutions,"},{"time":655000,"text":"and there are predictable solutions."},{"time":658000,"text":"I've hinted at them: education"},{"time":660000,"text":"and also economic opportunity."},{"time":663000,"text":"So of course, when you educate a girl,"},{"time":666000,"text":"she tends to get married later on in life,"},{"time":669000,"text":"she tends to have kids later on in life, she tends to have fewer kids,"},{"time":672000,"text":"and those kids that she does have,"},{"time":674000,"text":"she educates them in a more enlightened fashion."},{"time":676000,"text":"With economic opportunity,"},{"time":678000,"text":"it can be transformative."}]},{"cues":[{"time":680000,"text":"Let me tell you about Saima."},{"time":682000,"text":"She lives in a small village outside Lahore, Pakistan."},{"time":686000,"text":"And at the time, she was miserable."},{"time":688000,"text":"She was beaten every single day"},{"time":690000,"text":"by her husband, who was unemployed."},{"time":692000,"text":"He was kind of a gambler type -- and unemployable, therefore --"},{"time":695000,"text":"and took his frustrations out on her."},{"time":697000,"text":"Well, when she had her second daughter,"},{"time":699000,"text":"her mother in-law told her son,"},{"time":702000,"text":"\"I think you'd better get a second wife."},{"time":704000,"text":"Saima's not going to produce you a son.\""},{"time":708000,"text":"This is when she had her second daughter."},{"time":710000,"text":"At the time, there was"},{"time":712000,"text":"a microlending group in the village"},{"time":714000,"text":"that gave her a 65-dollar loan."},{"time":717000,"text":"Saima took that money,"},{"time":720000,"text":"and she started an embroidery business."},{"time":723000,"text":"The merchants liked her embroidery; it sold very well,"},{"time":725000,"text":"and they kept asking for more."},{"time":727000,"text":"And when she couldn't produce enough,"},{"time":729000,"text":"she hired other women in the village."},{"time":731000,"text":"Pretty soon she had 30 women in the village"},{"time":734000,"text":"working for her embroidery business."},{"time":736000,"text":"And then,"},{"time":738000,"text":"when she had to transport all of the embroidery goods"},{"time":741000,"text":"from the village to the marketplace,"},{"time":743000,"text":"she needed someone to help her do the transport,"},{"time":745000,"text":"so she hired her husband."},{"time":747000,"text":"So now they're in it together."},{"time":749000,"text":"He does the transportation and distribution,"},{"time":751000,"text":"and she does the production and sourcing."},{"time":753000,"text":"And now they have a third daughter,"},{"time":756000,"text":"and the daughters, all of them, are being tutored in education"},{"time":759000,"text":"because Saima knows what's really important."}]},{"cues":[{"time":762000,"text":"Which brings me to the final element, which is education."},{"time":766000,"text":"Larry Summers, when he was chief economist at the World Bank,"},{"time":769000,"text":"once said that, \"It may well be"},{"time":772000,"text":"that the highest return on investment"},{"time":774000,"text":"in the developing world"},{"time":776000,"text":"is in girls' education.\""},{"time":779000,"text":"Let me tell you about Beatrice Biira."},{"time":781000,"text":"Beatrice was living in Uganda"},{"time":784000,"text":"near the Congo border,"},{"time":786000,"text":"and like Dai Manju, she didn't go to school."},{"time":788000,"text":"Actually, she had never been to school,"},{"time":791000,"text":"not to a lick, one day."},{"time":793000,"text":"Her parents, again, said,"},{"time":795000,"text":"\"Why should we spend the money on her?"},{"time":797000,"text":"She's going to spend most of her life lugging water back and forth.\""},{"time":800000,"text":"Well, it just so happens, at that time,"},{"time":803000,"text":"there was a group in Connecticut"},{"time":806000,"text":"called the Niantic Community Church Group in Connecticut."},{"time":809000,"text":"They made a donation to an organization"},{"time":811000,"text":"based in Arkansas"},{"time":813000,"text":"called Heifer International."},{"time":815000,"text":"Heifer sent two goats to Africa."},{"time":818000,"text":"One of them ended up with Beatrice's parents,"},{"time":821000,"text":"and that goat had twins."},{"time":823000,"text":"The twins started producing milk."},{"time":825000,"text":"They sold the milk for cash."},{"time":827000,"text":"The cash started accumulating,"},{"time":829000,"text":"and pretty soon the parents said,"},{"time":831000,"text":"\"You know, we've got enough money. Let's send Beatrice to school.\""},{"time":834000,"text":"So at nine years of age,"},{"time":836000,"text":"Beatrice started in first grade --"},{"time":838000,"text":"after all, she'd never been to a lick of school --"},{"time":840000,"text":"with a six year-old."},{"time":842000,"text":"No matter, she was just delighted to be in school."},{"time":844000,"text":"She rocketed to the top of her class."},{"time":846000,"text":"She stayed at the top of her class"},{"time":849000,"text":"through elementary school, middle school,"},{"time":851000,"text":"and then in high school,"},{"time":853000,"text":"she scored brilliantly on the national examinations"},{"time":856000,"text":"so that she became the first person in her village,"},{"time":859000,"text":"ever, to come to the United States"},{"time":861000,"text":"on scholarship."},{"time":863000,"text":"Two years ago,"},{"time":865000,"text":"she graduated from Connecticut College."},{"time":868000,"text":"On the day of her graduation,"},{"time":870000,"text":"she said, \"I am the luckiest girl alive"},{"time":873000,"text":"because of a goat.\""},{"time":875000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":877000,"text":"And that goat was $120."}]},{"cues":[{"time":879000,"text":"So you see how transformative"},{"time":882000,"text":"little bits of help can be."},{"time":884000,"text":"But I want to give you a reality check."},{"time":887000,"text":"Look: U.S. aid, helping people is not easy,"},{"time":890000,"text":"and there have been books that have criticized U.S. aid."},{"time":893000,"text":"There's Bill Easterly's book."},{"time":895000,"text":"There's a book called \"Dead Aid.\""},{"time":897000,"text":"You know, the criticism is fair;"},{"time":899000,"text":"it isn't easy."},{"time":901000,"text":"You know, people say how"},{"time":903000,"text":"half of all water well projects, a year later, are failed."},{"time":905000,"text":"When I was in Zimbabwe,"},{"time":907000,"text":"we were touring a place with the village chief --"},{"time":909000,"text":"he wanted to raise money for a secondary school --"},{"time":912000,"text":"and there was some construction a few yards away,"},{"time":914000,"text":"and I said, \"What's that?\""},{"time":916000,"text":"He sort of mumbled."},{"time":918000,"text":"Turns out that it's a failed irrigation project."},{"time":920000,"text":"A few yards away was a failed chicken coop."},{"time":923000,"text":"One year, all the chickens died, and no one wanted to put the chickens in there."},{"time":926000,"text":"It's true, but we think that you don't through the baby out with the bathwater;"},{"time":929000,"text":"you actually improve."},{"time":931000,"text":"You learn from your mistakes, and you continuously improve."}]},{"cues":[{"time":934000,"text":"We also think that individuals"},{"time":936000,"text":"can make a difference, and they should,"},{"time":939000,"text":"because individuals, together,"},{"time":941000,"text":"we can all help create a movement."},{"time":944000,"text":"And a movement of men and women"},{"time":946000,"text":"is what's needed to bring about social change,"},{"time":948000,"text":"change that will address"},{"time":951000,"text":"this great moral challenge."},{"time":953000,"text":"So then, I ask,"},{"time":956000,"text":"what's in it for you?"},{"time":958000,"text":"You're probably asking that. Why should you care?"},{"time":961000,"text":"I will just leave you with two things."},{"time":963000,"text":"One is that research shows"},{"time":966000,"text":"that once you have"},{"time":968000,"text":"all of your material needs taken care of --"},{"time":971000,"text":"which most of us, all of us, here in this room do --"},{"time":974000,"text":"research shows that"},{"time":976000,"text":"there are very few things in life"},{"time":978000,"text":"that can actually elevate your level of happiness."},{"time":981000,"text":"One of those things"},{"time":983000,"text":"is contributing to a cause larger than yourself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":988000,"text":"And the second thing,"},{"time":990000,"text":"it's an anecdote that I'll leave you with."},{"time":992000,"text":"And that is the story"},{"time":994000,"text":"of an aid worker in Darfur."},{"time":997000,"text":"Here was a woman"},{"time":999000,"text":"who had worked in Darfur,"},{"time":1001000,"text":"seeing things that no human being should see."},{"time":1005000,"text":"Throughout her time there,"},{"time":1007000,"text":"she was strong, she was steadfast."},{"time":1010000,"text":"She never broke down."},{"time":1013000,"text":"And then she came back to the United States"},{"time":1015000,"text":"and was on break, Christmas break."},{"time":1017000,"text":"She was in her grandmother's backyard,"},{"time":1020000,"text":"and she saw something that made her break down in tears."},{"time":1024000,"text":"What that was"},{"time":1026000,"text":"was a bird feeder."},{"time":1029000,"text":"And she realized that she had the great fortune"},{"time":1032000,"text":"to be born in a country"},{"time":1034000,"text":"where we take security for granted,"},{"time":1037000,"text":"where we not only can feed, clothe"},{"time":1039000,"text":"and house ourselves,"},{"time":1042000,"text":"but also provide for wild birds"},{"time":1045000,"text":"so they don't go hungry in the winter."},{"time":1049000,"text":"And she realized that with that great fortune"},{"time":1052000,"text":"comes great responsibility."},{"time":1055000,"text":"And so, like her,"},{"time":1058000,"text":"you, me,"},{"time":1060000,"text":"we have all won the lottery of life."},{"time":1063000,"text":"And so the question becomes:"},{"time":1065000,"text":"how do we discharge that responsibility?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1068000,"text":"So, here's the cause."},{"time":1070000,"text":"Join the movement."},{"time":1072000,"text":"Feel happier and help save the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1075000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1077000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}